lyrics:
[Verse]
In the new business world we navigate
Opportunities knocking, we innovate
With dreams in our hearts, we take the leap
And embrace the challenges we're set to meet

[Chorus]
Oh, the new business world, it's ours to shape
Together we'll conquer, no limit nor escape
With passion and drive, our spirits unfurled
We thrive in this ever-changing new business world
